dct_title_s: Bosnia and Herzegovina city graphic 1:10,000. Sokolac. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Sokolac. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevation. This sheet falls within NK 34-1, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2882IV, M709, 1:50,000. "Map information as of 1994." "Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50." "Printed by DMAHTC 4-95." With a glossary. "This map is red-light readable."
